reviewText: This is an amazing document of times past. The black and white video is low resolution, the sound quality is variable, and this is the Cramps way, way, way before any gold lame. The stage they are performing on is approximately 2" high, the dancing and socializing psychiatric hospital patients are part of the show, there are very young, totally drunk SF/LA punks here and there - and this is the punkest thing you will ever see. Period.
